    <p style="color: #000000;" > Just Environmental Services ( Pty) Ltd, a private limited company services many retail, commercial, Medical and educational sites in KZN on a daily basis. With over 41 years of experience in the Pest control and Hygiene field. We specialise in providing our clients with tailored service contracts at affordable prices. Our clients benefit from a unique service that is tailored to each customer’s needs. Quality of service and commitment of the directors and staff have ensured that our customer retention is the highest in the pest control industry.</p> 
        <p style="color: #000000">Just Environmental Services is a member of South African Pest Control and the Pest control Federation of South Africa, which means that we keep up to date with any new rules and regulations in the industry. All equipment used at customers premises like ULV cold Foggers, Hot Foggers, electronic Fly control units are regularly tested and serviced six monthly. We use environmentally friendly preparations with a&nbsp; registration Number which have been registered with the Department of Agriculture.  Our Staff are regularly trained in the form of workshops and monthly toolbox talks to keep up to date with new rules and regulations.
          The Company has enjoyed steady growth based on quality of service and customer satisfaction, ensuring that customers enjoy personalised attention at all times. All customer complaints are addressed within 24 hours.</p>
